Contact information
    Michio Katouda (mkatouda@riken.jp)

Directory structure
src: source files of NTChem/RI-MP2
config: machine specific configurations files
tests: some examples of NTChem/RI-MP2 jobs

How to install NTChem/RI-MP2
./configure 
 --scratch=[dir path]                set the default scratch directory path 
 --lapack=[file path]                (option) set the file path for LAPACK library
 --lapack95=[file path]              (option) set the file path for LAPACK95 library
 --blas=[file path]                  (option) set the file path for BLAS library
 --atras=[file path]                 (option) set the file path for ATLAS library
 --mpi=[MPI prefix path]             if you use MPI, 
                                     set the prefix path where MPI is installed.
                                     if you use TCGMSG instead of MPI, this option has no meaning.
 --help                              show the help message


make
make install PREFIX=[dir]
